text: Poliaenus abietis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Tyson in 1968. It is known from the United States.BioLib.cz - Poliaenus abietis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Pogonocherini Category:Beetles described in 1968
